{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Unseen is a deeply atmospheric horror game that blends first and second-person perspectives to immerse you in a chilling and emotional journey.\u00a0</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as Sophie, a blind young girl who must rely on her best friend, Teddy, to navigate the dark, perilous halls of a creepy mansion. Each creak of the floorboards and whisper in the shadows could be your salvation\u2014or your doom.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2526310/extras/Unseen_1.gif?t=1736785062\" /><br>Blind, but not powerless</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find creative ways to overcome the challenges of your condition. Your instincts and your trusty teddy bear are your only tools for survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2526310/extras/011351-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1736785062\" /><br>A mansion full of secrets</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unearth the tragic past hidden within its walls as you piece together the events that led to its haunting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2526310/extras/Unseen_3.gif?t=1736785062\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Psychological terror</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your senses deceive you. What is real, and what is not?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2526310/extras/Unseen_4.gif?t=1736785062\" /><br>No escape, only survival</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Face your sinister captors and the horrors of the mansion. Can you uncover the truth before it\u2019s too late? No one ever escaped, will you be the first one?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_i